hopobject.body: Who would I report to? ciproxin 250 mg posologia cistite After working hard as a model from the age of 15, and then presenting on television (most famously on Popstars), Chung became known for “floating around and just going to parties”, which she says is exactly what she did not want to be known for. She now presents the music programme Fuse News in America and is designing an eye make-up range with the cult beauty brand Eyeko.
